GTP Backend API Gateway
 1.0.0 
OAS 3.0
🌟 Unified API Gateway for GTP Backend Microservices 🌟

This gateway provid=s a single entry point to all backend microservices in the GTP ecosystem. It handles routing, rate limiting, CORS, and provides a unified interface for frontend applications.

🎯 Available Services
🎫 Jira Trigger Service - Create and manage Jira issues
🤖 Chat Agent Service - AI-powered chat interactions
✅ Approval Service - Slack approval workflows
📦 Onboarding Service - Service catalog and onboarding
📊 ScoreCard Service - Service quality scorecards
🔍 SonarShell Service - SonarCloud automation
🔐 Security
Rate limiting: 100 requests per minute (configurable)
CORS enabled for configured origins
JWT authentication support (optional)
📝 Notes
All routes are prefixed with the service name (e.g., /jira/*, /chat/*)

